      "- Claude Code v2.1.170 - Model id: glm-5.1 - /effort ultracode: accepted - Real Workflow(...) tool invocation: accepted - Minimal dynamic workflow: 1 agent, completed in 11 seconds, result OK",
      "This confirms the runtime path works. Larger real-world workflows still need broader testing across repositories, task shapes, and Coding Plan tiers."
    ]
